[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ね、ねぇイクセくん。\n本当にこんなことしちゃっていいの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "ああ。こいつが作戦の鍵となるんだ。\n頑張って手を動かそうぜ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ。最初の手間がすべての効果を決めるのだもの。\nこの地味な工程すら愛おしいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "で、でも、こんなにたくさん……大丈夫かな？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "何を言ってるんだ、ロロナ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "今はこんなにたくさんあるように見えるが、\n処理しちまえば残るのはほんの一握りなんだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "そいつを薄めて使ってやれば、どんなものにも\nすごい効果を発揮するんだぜ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "テス",
		"romanized_name": "Tess",
		"model_path_hash": "7713659418971358664",
		"text": "へぇ……そんなもんなんだね～",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1974319971304968741",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ええ。そんなものよ。\nもっとも、私もここまで本格的に扱ったことはないのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "だからね……久々にわくわくしているの。\nこれを使って、どんな効果を引き出せるのかしらって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "テス",
		"romanized_name": "Tess",
		"model_path_hash": "7713659418971358664",
		"text": "クリセルダがそこまで言うなら、楽しみだなぁ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1974319971304968741",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "それはそうと、テスさんはここで\nお手伝いしてていいんですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "テスさんが勤めてるカフェのほうは\n大丈夫なのかなって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "テス",
		"romanized_name": "Tess",
		"model_path_hash": "7713659418971358664",
		"text": "うふふ、大丈夫。せっかくクリセルダに\n頼まれたんだし、盗める機会だしね～！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1974319971304968741",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "ははっ！　盗めるもんなら盗んでみろよな！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "なんにせよ、こいつはデカいヤマだ！\nロロナ、俺たちの人生賭けて全力を出すぞ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ええっ。わたしはイクセくんみたいには\n人生賭けていないよ……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "いいからいいから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "聞いたか。\n奴らはやはり、何か怪しげなものを作っているようだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "何よりあのクリセルダが関わっている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "何をしているのか、皆目見当もつかないが、\n恐ろしい効果を持つ何かを流通させる気では……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "ハハッ。まったく健気なもんだぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "呑気だな。私は奴を調査するよう伝えたはずだが？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "ああ、したよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "ひゃあ！　こ、これ本当に大丈夫なの！？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ、素敵ね。\n私の渇望を優しく激しく宥めてくれるよう……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "も、もう猶予は与えん！　奴のこれまでの動きから、\n企みの概要は少なからず掴めているはずだろう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "ああ。だからこそだよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "な……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "これ以上つつくのは野暮ってもんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ロロライナ・フリクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Rororina Fryxell",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "通称「ロロナ」。パイを作るのが好きな錬金術士。\nカフェ「星の繭」で働いている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "イクセル・ヤーン",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel Jahnn",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ロロナの幼馴染。カフェ「星の繭」では料理担当。\n料理やその素材へのこだわりが強く、熱血漢",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]